7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Rank Tracker and Surfer SEO share a solid foundation of core features including Keyword Research, Competitor Analysis, Serp Analysis, Reporting. Where Rank Tracker pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Rank Tracking, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Surfer SEO uniquely offers Site Audit and Content Optimization and Ai Writing and Api Access, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Rank Tracker holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Surfer SEO scores 8/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Rank Tracker offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Surfer SEO's starting price of $99/mo. Rank Tracker has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Surfer SEO does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
